1 to be applied to the driver’s side window to identify this exemption.
2 (8)(7) Any motor vehicle, registered and garaged within this state, whose sole purpose is
3 to provide executive security to persons within this state. The owner(s) of the vehicle shall first
4 seek and obtain written permission from the local police chief where the vehicle is garaged and
5 registered before the waiver is granted.
6 SECTION 2. This act shall take effect upon passage.
